The paper discusses the use of deep learning methods, specifically convolutional neural networks, for medical image segmentation, with a focus on brain pathology segmentation in MRI. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE), with potential relevance to multimedia (cs.MM) due to the use of MRI images.
